"classic high-quality toys.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"A little overview: Mother Heidi is always taking care of her family and "
"keeps the house clean and nicely decorated. Father Harlin enjoys planning "
"all the fun community events in Calico Village. Sister Bell is very cheerful "
"and likes having\n"
"fun with her family and friends. Brother Skip is a great soccer player and "
"is on his school’s team."
